reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Venom action figure!
reviews.reviewText: This is super realistic and very cool because it has different pieces such as hands faces… another thing that is very cool is that it can bend into so many different poses. However, when I first bought this one, the neck broke off the first day, my son had it, even though he was very gentle with it, and then the second one we’ve gotten is not very sturdy and doesn’t hold the positions that you’re trying to pose them in very well, it definitely is extremely realistic and cool looking. I just wish it was sturdier and made a little bit better.
